---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — AAA Devs">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="AAA Devs" class="h-auto w-48 max-w-full sm:w-56" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-text-muted">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>These terms govern your use of this website (aaadevs.com), the studio showcase of AAA Devs. By accessing or using the site, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site. Our individual products are operated on their own websites (for example, <a href="https://troniti.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">troniti.com</a>) and are governed by their own separate terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Use of Site</h2>
        <p>You may view this site for informational purposes. You agree not to misuse the site, attempt to disrupt its operation, or use it in violation of applicable law.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Accounts</h2>
        <p>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, design, and code are the property of AAA Devs. You may not copy, modify, or distribute any part of our services without permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Our services are provided "as is" without warranties. AAA Devs is not liable for any damages arising from the use of our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Reach us at <a href="mailto:ahmlvs@aaadevs.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">ahmlvs@aaadevs.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
